    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Sphinx_rtd_theme Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>sphinx_rtd_theme</application> module is a Sphinx theme
designed to provide a great reader experience for documentation users on
both desktop and mobile devices. This theme is used primarily on Read the
Docs but can work with any Sphinx project.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

